  <description>

<![CDATA[

  <p>

	  A distributed store based on a replicated segment architecture using
	  a Read One Write All Available (ROWAA) strategy.  This project is
	  designed to layer over the <code>dbCache</code> module and provide
	  the foundation for a distributed database.  This module provides the
	  peer discover, lock server, client/server partition, and replication
	  features of a distributed database.  An integration with jdbm(2.x) is
	  planned to support a Data2.0 GOM distributed high availabilty platform.

  </p>

]]>

